OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry
OL,6,Fovernight with clear spells, though
OL,7,Fpatchy low cloud bringing misty
OL,8,Fconditions over some hills. Blustery
OL,9,Faround coasts and over the mountains.
OL,10,FA rather chilly night with pockets of
OL,11,Fgrass frost possible in sheltered
OL,12,Frural areas.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FEarly cloud soon lifting to
OL,15,Fleave a fine day. After a cool start,
OL,16,Fsoon feeling warm with spells of
OL,17,Fstrong April sunshine despite the
OL,18,Fwind. Sunshine turning hazier later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
